---
title: Roasted Cauliflower Biryani with Currants & Almonds
description: Curry on rice is all well and good, but when the rice itself is cooked with the curry paste? Now that’s magical.
Studded with sweet currants, refreshing coriander and roasted cauliflower, this dish packs flavour in every bite.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

*Keep an eye out... Due to sourcing challenges over the Christmas period, some of the fresh ingredients you receive may be slightly different to what’s pictured. Don’t worry, your recipe will be just as delicious!*
